text: Nadia Germonpré (born 1933) is a Belgian road cyclist. At the 1960 Belgian National Road Race Championships, she won the bronze medal. She represented Belgium at the 1958 UCI Road World Championships, 1959 UCI Road World Championships, and 1960 UCI Road World Championships. == References == Category:1933 births Category:Belgian cyclists Category:Living people
